{"tid":1893561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際] 中共恐嚇捷克政要，若夠膽訪台將會報復捷克企業","createTime":"2020-02-23T10:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T13:25:03.000Z","uid":114580,"like":222,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"dea8973c98f5a5576f232aa5b4332d79ec9dbcdf","tid":1893561,"uid":114580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"見未有人post，RT煲一煲<br />\n<br />\n捷克共和國參議院議長Jaroslav Kundera生前原有意訪問台灣，中國駐布拉格大使館在1月10日寄送一封信函給捷克總統辦公室，揚言若Kundera訪問台灣，他們會點名對付捷克大型企業如Skoda、捷信，及琴廠Petrof Pianos。<br />\n<br />\nKundera今年1月過身，生前與台灣交好。現任總統奶共，議長淆底，剩返布拉格市長Zdenek Hrib（post pooh相果個，後生果陣去台灣做交換生）企硬<br />\n<br />\ncontext:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/_JakubJanda/status/1230747496822894595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_JakubJanda%2Fstatus%2F1230747496822894595&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAymo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=f3f11cda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_JakubJanda%2Fstatus%2F1230747496822894595&h=00192e04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/_JakubJanda/status/1230747496822894595</a><br />\n信:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BethanyAllenEbr/status/1230607293722615826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBethanyAllenEbr%2Fstatus%2F1230607293722615826&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAymo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=f83662ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBethanyAllenEbr%2Fstatus%2F1230607293722615826&h=8dde586f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BethanyAllenEbr/status/1230607293722615826</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1230161504294580224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1230161504294580224&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAymo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=37f4030a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1230161504294580224&h=7